<template>
  <component :is="tag" :href="href" :class="className"><slot></slot></component>
</template>

<script>
import classNames from 'classnames';

const DropdownItem = {
  props: {
    tag: {
      type: String,
      default: "a"
    },
    href: {
      type: String,
      default: "#"
    },
    disabled: {
      type: Boolean,
      default: false
    },
    active: {
      type: Boolean,
      default: false
    }
  },
  computed: {
    className() {
      return classNames(
        'dropdown-item',
        this.disabled ? 'disabled' : '',
        this.active ? 'active' : ''
      );
    }
  }
};

export default DropdownItem;
export { DropdownItem as mdbDropdownItem };
</script>

<style scoped>
</style>
